{"_id":"N6BKJKTPchzWSg3k","name":"藥物抗性","type":"perk","img":"modules/fallout_zh-TW/images/perk/CHEM%20RESISTANT.jpg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">在等級 1 的時候，當決定你是否會對化學藥品上癮時，要少擲一次 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">，最低為 0。</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-cf420230-7fff-2735-677a-a89196917740\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">在等級 2 時，你不會對化學藥品上癮。每當你使用這個輔助能力時，等級要求增加 4。</span></p>","favorite":false,"rank":{"max":2,"value":1,"levelStart":1,"levelIncrease":0},"requirements":"耐力 7, 等級 1+"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"xWJLZwu5IRU1lva8":3},"flag