{"_id":"XzHnmXX2JEnCZhsU","name":"黑寡婦/少女殺手","type":"perk","img":"modules/fallout_zh-TW/images/perk/BLACK%20WIDOW_LADY%20KILLER.jpg","data":{"description":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-00ab52e6-7fff-f744-8141-e89825401642\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">黑寡婦輔助能力影響男性和男性角色，而少女殺手輔助能力影響女性和女性角色&mdash;它們在其他方面是相同的。當你試圖通過基於魅力的技能檢定來影響一個所選性別的角色時，你可以重新滾動 1d20。此外，你的攻擊會對所選性別的角色造成 +1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> 的額外傷害。</span></span></p>","favorite":false,"rank":{"max":1,"value":1,"levelStart":1,"levelIncrease":0},"requirements":"魅力 6"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"xWJLZwu5IRU1lva8":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b4kctjhlqt5gxksZ","name":"水男孩/女孩","type":"perk","img":"modules/fallout_zh-TW/images/perk/AQUABOY_AQUAGIRL.jpg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">水是你的盟友。在 1 級時，你在受輻射的水中游泳時不再受到輻射傷害，而且你可以屏住呼吸的時間是正常的兩倍。</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-fe7e9b4c-7fff-d4cd-141d-94bb933cb78d\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">在 2 級時，當你被淹沒在水下時，敵人檢測你的難度會增加 +2。每次你獲得這個輔助能力，等級要求增加 3。</span></p>","favorite":false,"rank":{"max":2,"value":1,"levelStart":1,"levelIncrease":0},"requirements":"耐力 5, 等級 1+"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"xWJLZwu5IRU1lva8":3},"flags":{}}
